 "lrc": "[00:01.20]Yeah\n[00:02.32]My soul lives in Seoul\n[00:04.40]But my heart lives wherever you call me from\n[00:09.46]안녕, 내 사랑\n[00:10.64]Can you hear me now?\n[00:12.00]Signal’s weak\n[00:12.40]But I feel you somehow\n[00:13.60]Time zones, touch screens\n[00:14.72]Different skies, same dreams\n[00:16.80]One, two, three, go\n[00:18.32]I wake up, grab my phone before I even breathe\n[00:20.96]Thirty-seven messages waiting there for me\n[00:23.20]Your morning is my midnight, my sunrise is your sleep\n[00:25.92]But your face on my screen makes the distance feel sweet\n[00:28.24]Wi-Fi acting crazy, signal dropping low\n[00:30.64]“Can you hear me, baby?” then the camera froze\n[00:32.96]Front cam, back cam, why am I showing the floor?\n[00:35.52]You laughing so hard, now I love you even more\n[00:38.00]Battery on red, charger disappeared\n[00:40.00]Wrong cable in my bag, same problem all year\n[00:42.64]Storage full again from the photos that you send\n[00:44.72]But I still save every selfie like I’ll never see you again\n[00:47.68]Shipping takes forever, plane tickets are high\n[00:49.76]Currency conversion got me asking why\n[00:53.46]Forms on the table, stamps in a line\n[00:54.48]But I’d cross every border just to call you mine\n[00:57.36]K-1, K-2, CR-1 too\n[00:59.20]Paperwork dancing like it’s got moves\n[01:01.44]Lost in translation, but I still choose you\n[01:03.84]Every little problem turns into something cute\n[01:06.66]My soul lives in Seoul\n[01:08.75]But my love goes worldwide\n[01:10.40]From your good morning\n[01:12.86]To my good night\n[01:17.29]We fight, we make up\n[01:18.88]Then we laugh on the phone\n[01:18.96]No matter where you are\n[01:19.07]You never feel alone\n[01:20.00]내 영혼은 서울에 살아\n[01:22.08]Ne yeonghoneun Seoul-e sara\n[01:24.72]But it finds you wherever you go\n[01:27.44]보고 싶어, my baby\n[01:29.68]Bogo sipeo, my baby\n[01:30.64]My soul lives in Seoul\n[01:31.52]Oh-oh-oh, Seoul to your heart\n[01:36.24]Oh-oh-oh, miles apart\n[01:36.48]Oh-oh-oh, still we glow\n[01:41.20]My soul lives in Seoul\n[01:42.39]Oh-oh-oh, call me again\n[01:45.52]Oh-oh-oh, don’t let it end\n[01:45.52]Oh-oh-oh, you already know\n[01:47.36]My soul lives in Seoul\n[01:52.04]Family asking questions, friends all in the chat\n[01:55.44]“Is the foreigner rich?” Baby, what is that?\n[01:57.68]Everybody thinks love comes with a golden crown\n[02:00.24]But we’re just counting coins till the next flight down\n[02:02.48]You send me a box, it arrives next year\n[02:05.04]Customs got me crying, but I smile when it’s here\n[02:07.04]T-shirts, snacks, letters, little things you drew\n[02:09.44]I keep them like treasure cause they came from you\n[02:11.76]Language barrier? We turn it into jokes\n[02:13.60]I say one wrong word and the whole call explodes\n[02:15.92]Different food, different rules, different ways to show we care\n[02:18.24]But your culture feels like music when you let me meet you there\n[02:21.20]Tired thumbs from typing all night\n[02:22.96]Tired voice from “one more call” till daylight\n[02:25.28]Missed calls, small fights, pride in the way\n[02:27.60]Then one heart emoji saves the whole day\n[02:29.84]You screenshot me sleeping, I screenshot you mad\n[02:32.96]We got duplicate pictures of the best days we had\n[02:35.60]Backup the memories, new phone, same us\n[02:38.08]Too many photos, not enough touch\n[02:39.84]My soul lives in Seoul\n[02:42.05]But my love goes worldwide\n[02:44.32]From your good morning\n[02:46.11]To my good night\n[02:47.90]We fight, we make up\n[02:50.14]Then we laugh on the phone\n[02:52.83]No matter where you are\n[02:54.40]You never feel alone\n[02:59.52]내 영혼은 서울에 살아\n[02:59.52]Ne yeonghoneun Seoul-e sara\n[02:59.68]But it finds you wherever you go\n[03:03.60]보고 싶어, my baby\n[03:06.34]Bogo sipeo, my baby\n[03:08.56]My soul lives in Seoul\n[03:11.70]야, 내 양말은 바닥에 한 번뿐이야\n[03:14.43]Ya, nae yangmareun badage han beonppuniya\n[03:21.27]Your hair is everywhere, girl, 진짜 장난 아니야\n[03:22.88]Jinjja jangnan aniya\n[03:23.36]설거지는 산처럼 쌓여 있는데\n[03:23.52]Seolgeojineun sancheoreom ssayeo inneunde\n[03:29.68]You say “oppa, later,” then you buy one more thing\n[03:32.96]뭐? 너는 돈 없다면서 치킨은 또 시켜\n[03:36.00]Mwo? Neoneun don eopdamyeonseo chicken-eun tto sikyeo\n[03:39.28]게임은 새로 사고 내 말은 또 미뤄\n[03:49.28]Game-eun saero sago nae mareun tto mirwo\n[03:49.92]내 머리카락? 사랑의 흔적이야\n[03:50.72]Nae meorikarak? Sarang-ui heunjeogiya\n[03:52.96]네 양말 냄새는 거의 전설이야\n[03:56.64]Okay, okay, maybe I’m messy\n[04:00.60]Maybe I shop when I’m stressy\n[04:05.04]You blame me for the belly\n[04:05.66]You made me love your food already\n[04:05.76]우리 둘 다 살쪘어, 하하, 괜찮아\n[04:16.64]Uri dul da saljjyeosseo, haha, gwaenchana\n[04:19.36]너의 나라, 나의 나라, 맛있잖아\n[04:20.48]Neoui nara, naui nara, masitjana\n[04:22.40]싸워도 웃고, 다시 안아\n[04:23.52]Ssawodo utgo, dasi ana\n[04:24.88]사랑은 배불러도 계속 가잖아\n[04:26.56]Dale, dale, mi amor, aunque lejos estamos\n[04:28.88]El vuelo cuesta caro, pero igual lo soñamos\n[04:31.12]Se cae la señal, pero sube el corazón\n[04:34.61]Tu voz en mi teléfono me cambia la canción\n[04:37.68]Cambio de moneda, papeles en la mesa\n[04:41.76]Visa, entrevista, paciencia y promesa\n[04:44.48]Tu familia pregunta, mis panas también\n[04:47.36]Pero nadie entiende lo que tú y yo tenemos, ven\n[04:49.76]Baila conmigo por la pantalla\n[04:52.28]Aunque la cámara nunca se halla\n[04:53.36]Batería baja, cargador perdido\n"
}